# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Crystal Clawz Social Studio — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE
# 1. Copy this file and rename the copy to:  .env.local
# 2. Fill in the values below (instructions for each one)
# 3. Never commit .env.local to git — it contains your secret keys
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE GEMINI API KEY (for AI content generation)
# Get this from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FIREBASE (for login + data storage)
#
# Steps to get these values:
#  1. Go to https://console.firebase.google.com
#  2. Create a project (or open your existing one)
#  3. Click the gear icon → Project Settings
#  4. Scroll down to "Your apps" → click the </> (Web) icon
#  5. Register the app, then copy the firebaseConfig values below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your-firebase-api-key
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your-project-id.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your-project-id.appspot.com
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your-sender-id
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your-app-id

